v%C5%A9/poem-h0jytt0r16CA91mIbSZ8GQ">Thương Ngô mộ vũ - 蒼梧暮雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Sa-qu%C3%A1-Gi%E1%BA%A3-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-tr%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-FHWlpMQQsSSm1ErZ-pRSsA">Trường Sa quá Giả Nghị trạch - 長沙過賈誼宅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-tOqeEdGQ0OZRwfU1Vi35GA">Lưu Trường Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-qu%E1%BA%ADn-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BB%AB-Th%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng/poem-TiyizL_yYIdXIMtmR4KK6A">Từ Thức động - 徐式洞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-qu%E1%BA%ADn-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-cAYfmQw9YZ3iSIfICIvyrw">Tương An quận vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Y%E1%BA%BFt-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%A1-H%E1%BB%93-Nh%E1%BB%AF-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-m%E1%BB%99-th%E1%BB%A9-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Ph%E1%BB%91-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-KioJZo86aVI8FwT-S6MYrA">Yết Phương Bá Hồ Nhữ Ngọc tiên sinh mộ, thứ Đông Phố nguyên vận - 謁方伯胡汝玉先生墓次東圃原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br></div>	</div>
